Affaire Liliane Bettencourt : François-Marie Banier convicted of exploitation of weakness
On Friday, the Nanterre Court of Justice decided to judge the artist François-Marie Banier in order to determine whether, as the daughter of billionaire Liliane Bettencourt claims, he took advantage of a weak moment of the eighty-year-olds to catch up with some of their assets.
