We have to stop the terrorists down there, she says.
Obama, who inherited two wars from his predecessor George W. Bush, the wars in Iraq and Afghanistan, tried on Thursday in Oslo to justify the use of force; a way of explaining his decision nine days ago to send 30,000 additional soldiers to Afghanistan.
